<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>NimbyGram</title>
  <style>
    /* Basic styling */
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #0070f3;
    }
    
    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
    }
    
    nav li {
      margin-left: 20px;
    }
    
    nav a {
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    nav a:hover {
      color: #0070f3;
    }
    
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .hero p {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #666;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
    }
    
    .search-form {
      display: flex;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .search-form input {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    
    .search-form button {
      background: #0070f3;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin: 60px 0;
    }
    
    .feature {
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .feature h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    
    footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">NimbyGram</div>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Login</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Find Planning Applications Near You</h1>
      <p>Search for planning applications, view details, and stay informed about developments in your area.</p>
      
      <form class="search-form">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your postcode or address">
        <button type="submit">Search</button>
      </form>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Find Applications</h3>
        <p>Search for planning applications by location, type, or keyword to stay informed about developments in your area.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>View on Map</h3>
        <p>See planning applications displayed on an interactive map to understand their location and context.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Get Notifications</h3>
        <p>Set up alerts for new planning applications in your area so you never miss important developments.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>NimbyGram aggregates planning application data from local authorities across the UK. Our platform makes it easy to search for applications, view details, and stay informed about developments that matter to you.</p>
      
      <p>Whether you're a homeowner concerned about nearby developments, a planning professional, or just curious about changes in your neighborhood, NimbyGram provides the information you need in an accessible format.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 NimbyGram. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    // Simple JavaScript to show the site is working
    document.querySelector('.search-form').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      alert('Search functionality will be available soon!');
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html> 